django-password-policies
========================

.. image:: https://travis-ci.org/tarak/django-password-policies.svg?branch=master
    :target: https://travis-ci.org/tarak/django-password-policies
.. image:: https://coveralls.io/repos/tarak/django-password-policies/badge.svg?branch=master
  :target: https://coveralls.io/r/tarak/django-password-policies?branch=master
.. image:: https://pypip.in/version/django-password-policies/badge.svg
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-password-policies/
    :alt: Latest Version
.. image:: https://pypip.in/download/django-password-policies/badge.svg
